## 2. Identifying Legacy MIT Versions

Over time, Gestura AI may publish documentation indicating which tags,
releases, or files are considered "Legacy MIT Versions" (for example,
by annotating Git tags or adding notes to release descriptions).

Until such a catalog is formally published, downstream users who
obtained the project under the MIT License may continue to rely on that
license for the relevant versions or files they received.

