## 3. PPL-3% for New Work

New work, features, and files added after the adoption of the
PPL-3% license are intended to be covered by the Prosocial Public
License – PPL-3% (Gestura AI / Stick-Gen Variant), subject to any
explicit exceptions or dual-licensing agreements made by Gestura AI.

See the LICENSE and LICENSE_PPL_README.md files for details on the
current primary license and how the PPL-3% model applies.
